pages-strings.Find what you're looking for in our deta:
Find what you're looking for in our detailed documentation and guides.

- Learn how to [get started](/jest/docs/en/getting-started.html) with Jest.
- [Troubleshoot](/jest/docs/en/troubleshooting.html) problems with Jest.
- Learn how to [configure Jest](/jest/docs/en/configuration.html).
- Look at the full [API Reference](/jest/docs/en/api.html).
pages-strings.Ask questions and find answers from othe:
Ask questions and find answers from other Jest users like you.

- Join the [#jest](https://discord.gg/MWRhKCj) channel on [Reactiflux](http://www.reactiflux.com/), a Discord community.
- Many members of the community use Stack Overflow. Read through the [existing questions](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/jestjs) tagged with **jestjs** or [ask your own](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ask)!
pages-strings.Find out what's new with Jest.\\n\\n- Fo:
Find out what's new with Jest.

- Follow [Jest](https://twitter.com/fbjest) on Twitter.
- Subscribe to the [Jest blog](/jest/blog/).
- Look at the [changelog](https://github.com/facebook/jest/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md).
pages-strings.Jest is worked on full-time by Facebook': Jest is worked on full-time by Facebook's JavaScript Foundation team. Team members are often around and available for questions.
pages-strings.Complete and easy to set-up JavaScript t: Complete and easy to set-up JavaScript testing solution. Works out of the box for any React project.
pages-strings.Fast interactive watch mode runs only te: Fast interactive watch mode runs only test files related to changed files and is optimized to give signal quickly.
pages-strings.Capture snapshots of React trees or othe: Capture snapshots of React trees or other serializable values to simplify testing and to analyze how state changes over time.
pages-strings.Jest is used by Facebook to test all Jav: Jest is used by Facebook to test all JavaScript code including React applications. One of Jest's philosophies is to provide an integrated \"zero-configuration\" experience. We observed that when engineers are provided with ready-to-use tools, they end up writing more tests, which in turn results in more stable and healthy code bases.
pages-strings.Jest parallelizes test runs across worke: Jest parallelizes test runs across workers to maximize performance. Console messages are buffered and printed together with test results. Sandboxed test files and automatic global state resets for every test so no two tests conflict with each other.
pages-strings.Easily create code coverage reports usin: Easily create code coverage reports using [`--coverage`](https://facebook.github.io/jest/docs/en/cli.html#coverage). No additional setup or libraries needed! Jest can collect code coverage information from entire projects, including untested files.
pages-strings.Jest is already configured when you use: Jest is already configured when you use [`create-react-app`](https://facebook.github.io/react/blog/2016/07/22/create-apps-with-no-configuration.html) or [`react-native init`](http://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/getting-started.html) to create your React and React Native projects. Place your tests in a `__tests__` folder, or name your test files with a `.spec.js` or `.test.js` extension. Whatever you prefer, Jest will find and run your tests.
pages-strings.You can try out a real version of Jest u: You can try out a real version of Jest using [repl.it](https://repl.it/languages/jest). Consider a function, `add()`, that adds two numbers. We can use a basic test in `add-test.js` to verify that 1 + 2 equals 3. Hit \"run\" to try it out!
pages-strings.Powerful [mocking library](/jest/docs/en: Powerful [mocking library](/jest/docs/en/mock-functions.html) for functions and modules. Mock React Native components using `jest-react-native`.
pages-strings.Jest works with any compile-to-JavaScrip: Jest works with any compile-to-JavaScript language and integrates seamlessly with [Babel](https://babeljs.io) and with TypeScript through [ts-jest](https://github.com/kulshekhar/ts-jest).
pages-strings.The Jest core team and contributors regu: The Jest core team and contributors regularly speak about Jest and Delightful JavaScript Testing. Check out our talks about [Building High-Quality JavaScript Tools](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PvabBs_utr8) at JSConf.eu 2017 or our talk about [Jest as a Platform](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NtjyeojAOBs) at ReactiveConf 2017.
pages-strings.Jest is used by teams of all sizes to te: Jest is used by teams of all sizes to test web applications, node.js services, mobile apps, and APIs.
pages-strings.We understand that reading through docs: We understand that reading through docs can be boring sometimes. Here is a community curated list of talks & videos around Jest.
